<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Password Reset - VOTE4ME</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A90D9 0%, #357ABD 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #4A90D9; color: white !important; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
        .button:hover { background: #357ABD; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .warning { color: #d9534f; font-weight: bold; }
        .code-box { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border: 1px dashed #ddd; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üó≥Ô∏è VOTE4ME</h1>
            <p>Secure Voting System</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
            <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to create a new password:</p>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
            </p>

            <p class="warning">‚è∞ This link will expire in {{expiresIn}}.</p>

            <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
            <div class="code-box">
                <code style="word-break: break-all;">{{resetUrl}}</code>
            </div>

            <p>If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from VOTE4ME voting system.</p>
            <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

